com.tupilabs.pbs.model

Class Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tupilabs.pbs.model.Job
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Job
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A PBS job. This job can be submitted to the PBS cluster, but its state is always detached. The information in a Job object is updated as you call service methods.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Bruno P. Kinoshita
